{"description": "The sequel to 'Talking Heads...'\n\nDesigning an REST api for your projects is difficult enough, implementing the api should be simple.\n\nBuilding a REST api is more then serialisation to JSON with Dancer2::Serializer::JSON or doing CRUD with Dancer2::Plugin::REST (which in so not RESTful, unlike it claims in the docs).\n\nUsing the Dancer2::Plugin::HTTP family of modules will help to implement your API design fully RFC compliant", "event": {"name": "London Perl Workshop 2015", "nickname": "london-perl-workshop-2015", "twitter": "LondonPerl", "url": "http://act.yapc.eu/lpw2015/"}, "favorite": "0", "file_date": "2016-12-10", "filename": "lpw2015-theo-van-hoesel-dancer2-rest-assured", "length": "53:59", "likes": "0", "recorded": "2015-12-12", "short_description": "The sequel to 'Talking Heads...' Designing an REST api for your projects is difficult enough, implementing the api should be sim", "speaker_twitters": " @Theo_vanHoesel", "speakers": {"theo-van-hoesel": {"episodes": [], "hosting": [], "info": {"city": "Zwolle", "country": "The Netherlands", "github": "vanHoesel", "gplus": "111485536112705772953", "name": "Theo van Hoesel", "slides": "http://www.slideshare.net/theovanhoesel", "twitter": "Theo_vanHoesel"}, "videos": [{"event": {"name": "London Perl Workshop 2015", "nickname": "london-perl-workshop-2015", "twitter": "LondonPerl", "url": "http://act.yapc.eu/lpw2015/"}, "filename": "lpw2015-theo-van-hoesel-dancer2-rest-assured", "recorded": "2015-12-12", "thumbnail_url": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/aL5rJvfwy1I/hqdefault.jpg", "title": "Dancer2 REST assured"}, {"event": {"name": "YAPC - European Perl Conference 2016", "nickname": "yapc-eu-2016", "twitter": "yapceu", "url": "http://act.yapc.eu/ye2016/"}, "filename": "theo-van-hoesel-making-the-first-hard-thing-easy-yapceurope-2016", "recorded": "2016-08-24", "thumbnail_url": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/H3vckSMhed4/hqdefault.jpg", "title": "Making the 'First Hard Thing' easy"}]}}, "tags": [], "thumbnail_ur